# 🏠 Auditora Home Inspection — Business Website

> **Live Site:** [auditora.ca](https://auditora.ca) &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Alias:** [auditorahomeinspection.ca](https://auditorahomeinspection.ca)

A fully custom, multi-page business website built from scratch for **Auditora Home Inspection** — a certified residential home inspection company serving Greater Vancouver, BC. Designed, developed, and deployed end-to-end with no frameworks or CMS.

---

## 📸 Preview

![Auditora Homepage](https://auditora.ca)

> Professional Home Inspections in Greater Vancouver 

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Vanilla HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript |
| **Fonts** | Google Fonts — Playfair Display + DM Sans |
| **Hosting** | Netlify (free tier, drag & drop deploy) |
| **DNS** | Netlify DNS via CanSpace registrar |
| **Booking** | Square Appointments (third-party embed) |
| **SSL** | Let's Encrypt via Netlify (auto-provisioned) |
| **Version Control** | Git + GitHub |

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
auditora/
│
├── index.html          # Homepage — hero, services, pricing, reviews, CTA
├── services.html       # Full breakdown of all 4 inspection types
├── pricing.html        # Pricing table + FAQ accordion
├── book.html           # Booking page — Square Appointments integration
├── about.html          # Inspector bio, credentials, tools, values
├── contact.html        # Contact form + phone/email links
├── privacy.html        # Privacy Policy (BC PIPA compliant)
├── terms.html          # Terms & Conditions
└── cancellation.html   # Cancellation Policy
```

---

## ✨ Features

- **9-page fully linked website** — every nav link, button, and footer link is functional
- **Responsive design** — mobile-first layout with hamburger nav for small screens
- **Scroll reveal animations** — IntersectionObserver-based fade-up animations throughout
- **Interactive pricing FAQ** — accordion expand/collapse, no libraries
- **Live phone & email links** — click-to-call and mailto on all pages
- **Square Appointments integration** — third-party booking system linked from book page
- **Legal pages** — Privacy Policy (BC PIPA), Terms & Conditions, Cancellation Policy
- **Custom DNS configuration** — both `auditora.ca` and `auditorahomeinspection.ca` connected via Netlify DNS
- **HTTPS / SSL** — auto-provisioned via Let's Encrypt through Netlify
- **SEO-ready** — semantic HTML, meta descriptions, clean URL structure, page titles

---

## 🎨 Design Decisions

- **Color palette:** Deep navy (`#0d1b2a`) + warm gold (`#c9973a`) — professional, trustworthy, premium
- **Typography:** Playfair Display (headings) paired with DM Sans (body) — editorial meets clean
- **Grid overlay + radial gradients** on hero sections for depth without images
- **Gold accent underline** on card hover — subtle, polished interaction detail
- **Trust bar** — HIABC, insured, thermal imaging credentials displayed prominently above the fold

---

## 🌐 Deployment

Deployed on **Netlify** via manual drag-and-drop upload.

**DNS Setup:**
- Domains registered through **CanSpace Solutions**
- Old conflicting `A records` (pointing to CanSpace's default IP `198.100.154.154`) removed
- Netlify NETLIFY records auto-configured for both apex and www
- SSL certificate provisioned after full DNS propagation (~12–24 hours)

---

## 📄 Pages Overview

### `/` — Homepage
Full business landing page. Hero with value proposition, trust bar, services preview, why choose us section, pricing table, client reviews, service area chips, and dual CTA.

### `/services` — Services
Detailed breakdown of all four inspection types: Full Home, Condo, Townhouse, and Pre-Listing. Each section includes a full includes checklist and booking CTA.

### `/pricing` — Pricing
Square footage–based pricing table ($399–$549+), what's always included grid, and an interactive FAQ accordion covering common client questions.

### `/book` — Book Online
Dedicated booking page with Square Appointments integration, step-by-step process guide, and sidebar with pricing, service area, and phone fallback.

### `/about` — About
Inspector biography, credential badges (HIABC, Carson Dunlop, insured, FLIR thermal), professional tools section, and core values.

### `/contact` — Contact
Contact form (name, phone, email, address, service type, message) with simulated submission state, plus direct phone/email cards.

### Legal Pages
`/privacy`, `/terms`, `/cancellation` — BC PIPA compliant privacy policy, inspection terms of service, and a tiered cancellation policy (48h / 24h / no-show).

---

## 🔧 Running Locally

No build step required — pure HTML/CSS/JS.


